citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at
4:15pm-4:54pm on 17-MAR-20.
Honked, knocked, called out loudly. Called number provided (voicemail full) and also sent a text message. Left a
door hanger with instructions to call home inspector.
